dc_creator_sm: Yolo County, Public Works Division, Planning Services
dc_description_s: This dataset represents the projected land-uses within Yolo County, California, as described in the county's General Plan. The General Plan can be accessed via the following URL: http://www.yolocounty.org/general-government/general-government-departments/county-administrator/general-plan-updateLatest data export occurred on March 10th. 2009. Data was mapped and provided by the Yolo County, Public Works Division
dc_title_s: 2030 General Land Use Plan, Yolo County, California, 2009
